  "title": "Bartender (Hotel Industry)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Mix and serve alcoholic beverages and cocktails.</li>\n  <li>Keep the bar area clean and sanitized at all times.</li>\n  <li>Support inventory management, monitor costs, and minimize wastage of bar supplies.</li>\n  <li>Engage with guests and deliver high-quality customer service.</li>\n  <li>Record guest orders and serve food and drinks accordingly.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum 1 year of working experience as Bartender</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication skills</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested applicants for the above advertised position(s), please kindly email an updated copy of your resume to: <strong>gs1@talenttradersg.com;</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA License No.: 13C6305</p>\n<p>Registration No.: R23117856 CHOE KIN MUN</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>For candidate who applied for the advertised position is deemed to have consented to us that we may collect, use or disclose your personal information for purpose in connection with the services provided by us.</p>",
